TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
Select 'SELECT /*+ index('|| Table_Name ||') */ ''' || Table_Name || ''' ,FILENAME, RECORDNUMBER, ' || REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(UPPER(replace( rk.FieldNameList , ',' , '||''~''||' )),'UPPER(',''),'LOWER(',''),')','') || ',' || Column_Name || ', ''' || Column_Name ||''''||',' ||fv.Conditionid ||','||fv.ISWARNINGONLY|| ' FROM ' || Table_Name || ' WHERE FILENAME = ''' || '$$filename' || ''' ' || ' AND nvl(IS_FILTERED,0)=0 '
From ALL_TAB_COLUMNS atc, TELS_CORE_FIELDVALIDATION fv, TELS_CORE_RECORDKEY rk Where substr(atc.Owner,1,4) = substr(User,1,4) And atc.Table_Name = '$$prestage_tablename' And atc.Column_Name Not in ('FILENAME','RECORDNUMBER') And fv.TableName = atc.Table_Name And fv.FieldName = atc.Column_Name And rk.TableName(+) = fv.TableName And rk.IsPrimaryRecordKey = 1 Order By Column_ID, FV.CONDITIONID DESC

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select to_char(lower(name)) as tcdatatypevalue, 'BusinessUnit' as tcdatatype from CS_BUSINESSUNIT@TC_LINK union select to_char(EVENTTYPEID) as tcdatatypevalue, 'EventType' as tcdatatype from CS_EVENTTYPE@TC_LINK union select to_char(lower(NAME)) as tcdatatypevalue,'ProcessingUnit' as tcdatatype from CS_PROCESSINGUNIT@TC_LINK union select to_char(lower(FIXEDVALUETYPEID)) as tcdatatypevalue, 'FixedValueType' as tcdatatype from CS_FIXEDVALUETYPE@TC_LINK f where f.REMOVEDATE = (Select max(removedate) from CS_PERIOD@TC_LINK) union select to_char(lower(CREDITTYPEID)) as tcdatatypevalue, 'CreditType' as tcdatatype from CS_CREDITTYPE@TC_LINK ct where ct.REMOVEDATE = (Select max(removedate) from CS_PERIOD@TC_LINK) union select to_char(lower(EARNINGGROUPID)) as tcdatatypevalue, 'EarningGroup' as tcdatatype from CS_EARNINGGROUP@TC_LINK eg where eg.removedate = (Select max(removedate) from CS_PERIOD@TC_LINK) union select to_char(lower(EARNINGCODEID)) as tcdatatypevalue, 'EarningCode' as tcdatatype from CS_EARNINGCODE@TC_LINK ec where ec.removedate = (Select max(removedate) from CS_PERIOD@TC_LINK) union select to_char(lower(NAME)) as tcdatatypevalue, 'Calendar' as tcdatatype from CS_CALENDAR@TC_LINK c where c.REMOVEDATE = (Select max(removedate) from CS_PERIOD@TC_LINK) union select to_char(lower(NAME)) as tcdatatypevalue, 'UnitType' as tcdatatype from CS_UNITTYPE@TC_LINK u where u.REMOVEDATE = (Select max(removedate) from CS_PERIOD@TC_LINK) union select to_char(lower(name)) as tcdatatypevalue, 'GenericClassifierType' as tcdatatype from CS_GENERICCLASSIFIERTYPE@TC_LINK union select to_char(lower(ReasonID)) as tcdatatypevalue, 'ReasonId' as tcdatatype from cs_reason@TC_LINK re where re.REMOVEDATE = (Select max(removedate) from CS_PERIOD@TC_LINK) union select to_char(lower(name)) as tcdatatypevalue, 'PeriodType' as tcdatatype from cs_periodtype@TC_LINK where REMOVEDATE = (Select max(removedate) from CS_PERIOD@TC_LINK)
